lead_paragraph: An Australian team full of rookies will be pushed blinking into the spotlight of the day-night test in Adelaide facing a huge task to prevent South Africa from completing an unprecedented series sweep on their home soil.

headline.print_headline: Raw Australia Seek to Reboot Under Adelaide Lights
